TITLE: Creating a Data Interval for a Sine Wave
DESCRIPTION: Generates a 1D array of data points representing a sine wave that moves over time. Uses an expression function to compute X and Y coordinates for 64 points.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unconed/mathbox/blob/master/docs/intro.md#2025-04-22_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
