TITLE: Defining a Camera in MathBox
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines the properties for the 'camera' primitive in the 'camera' module of MathBox. It allows for configuring a camera instance or proxy with various positioning and orientation options.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unconed/mathbox/blob/master/docs/primitives.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: markdown
