SOURCE: https://github.com/unconed/mathbox/blob/master/docs/primitives.md#2025-04-22_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
{
  blending: "normal",
  classes: [],
  closed: false,
  color: "rgb(128, 128, 128)",
