TITLE: Generating Text Values in MathBox with JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: JavaScript code that creates a text array containing numeric values from 0 to 255. This array will be used as the source for text sprites in the retext shader operation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unconed/mathbox/blob/master/docs/shaders.md#2025-04-22_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
mathbox
.text({
  width: 256,
  weight: 'bold',
  expr: function (emit, i) { emit(i); },
});
```

